---
import ScreenshotGallery from "../ScreenshotGallery.astro";
---

<section id="dashboard" class="section section-terminal">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">THE DASHBOARD</div>
    <h2 class="section-h2">
      A local dashboard that answers the only question that matters:
      <span class="ink">where did it go?</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="section-lede">
      The TUI and desktop app share the same archive, filters, refresh logic, Usage view, Insights, and report
      flow. In the terminal, press <kbd>1</kbd>-<kbd>5</kbd> for time ranges, <kbd>u</kbd> for Usage,
      <kbd>i</kbd> for Insights, and <kbd>e</kbd> for reports.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="landing-gallery-stack">
    <ScreenshotGallery platform="desktop" />
    <ScreenshotGallery platform="tui" />
  </div>
</section>
